channel.title: Project Legacy [Release] LINKED FIXED!
channel.description:
[center][size=10pt]PROJECT LEGACY 317[/size][/center]
Leech the fuck out of it, it hasn't got Anti-Leech. I know, it isn't the best release of PI ever.. But I have added a lot into this to make it good. [b]COMMENT OTHERWISE I'LL REMOVE LINKS!!!!!!!!!![/b]
#- Perfect Pking # - Great Minigames # - Flawless Combat System - Perfect timing, animations and calculations # - Anti-Dupe # - Stable Server Economy # - Insane gameframe changer, 474, 525 and 562. # - Great Starter # - Lots of Monsters to battle against, by yourself or with Clans! # - Tons of Minigames # - Fixed clan chat bug # - Fixed pest control dupes
[B][U]Main Server Features [/U][/B] - Great well-spaced out home, (Edgeville) - All 19 skills fully working - Perfect Pvp armours - Perfect Multi barrage, blitz and auto-casting - Perfect Hybrid switching - Lunar magics 100% - Perfected Spirit Shields, like RuneScape - Every single SkillCape emote working - Lots of minigames: Barrows, Pest Control, Recipe For Disaster, Tzhaar and Duel Arena - 100% Slayer, with working tasks and 3 floors - Perfect mage, range and melee following - Great leveling, ::Pure command to get pking, or additionally level up - Stable leveling - Great money making - A perfected Skilling area for skillers to enjoy! - Tons of more things to do then the same old, bosses, monsters and minigames. We have more teleports, new Minigames, perfected skilling area and various city teleports - 100% Working Godwars. Correct bosses etc etc - Fixed 98% of all items, they're all in the correct item slot. Removed RFD and added the gloves into PC shop, removed turmoil (Easy to add), cleaned the commands.Java up a bit. Fixed NPC drops, fixed the shops contents, also I have fixed 30% of the NPCs animations and gfxs, added better weapon formulas.
